{"tid":1905731,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[利記又贏] 高普：可自在地踢波了","createTime":"2020-03-01T12:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T07:14:36.000Z","uid":60281,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb9e06b16c451a0e58092dbfb731e2fd72b1848","tid":1905731,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200301/s00006/d4e77533ef643d7d5fc28158f935a7bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200301%2Fs00006%2Fd4e77533ef643d7d5fc28158f935a7bb.jpg&h=5162e9ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利物浦今季英超破不敗身，跨季聯賽44連勝亦斷纜。紅軍今晨作客賽前排尾二的屈福特，爆大冷慘吞3蛋敗走。相隔1個月復任正選的紅軍中堅洛夫雲，被敵鋒迪尼稱是死穴，惟客軍領隊高普預料總有一天輸波，「今後我們可以再次自在地踢波」。<br />\n<br />\n今季英超主場曾挫曼聯及狼隊的屈福特，此役再度發威，憑翼鋒伊斯美拿沙亞於54和60分鐘梅開二度，並在72分鐘助攻隊長迪尼，繼2015年12月後，再次以3：0淨勝客軍「一哥」利物浦，取得近6場英超首勝，賽後28戰得27分，由尾二暫時升上尾四的第17位，與尾三般尼茅夫同分，護級形勢續險惡。紅軍失分後續得79分，雖仍領先踢少一場的次席球隊曼城22分，但今季18連勝終斷，爭取打破阿仙奴在2004年，創下的跨季49場連勝等多項英超紀錄則無疾而終。<br />\n<br />\n由於紅軍後衛祖高美斯受傷，洛夫雲此役復任正選，伙拍華基爾雲迪積克鎮守中路。洛夫雲此役面對迪尼相當吃力，後者賽後亦坦言針對洛夫雲埋手：「雲迪積克是世界級中堅，對我而言是世界五大後衛，很難在他身上取得好處，自然要向較弱的埋手。我知道洛夫雲打算與我硬碰，這正合我意，跟我硬碰就要預備好這夜會很難受。」<br />\n<br />\n利物浦突遭挫敗，一直避談紀錄的主帥高普說：「落敗當然傷心，但我們從不談紀錄，只是傳媒在關注。我們一直知道總會輸波，我會看得正面點，因今後我們可以再次自在地踢波了，不用再守着什麼紀錄，只需要努力贏波。」紅軍之前歐聯16強首回合曾敗走馬德里體育會，而周二足總盃16強將作客大戰車路士。"},{"pid":"00b383f78729e7955d3c53a46dadd98073c35899","tid":1905731,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"自在足球<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04006e0be0a72597710f9729d2d30e5f5bdd29f","tid":1905731,"uid":283207,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/57/17486338.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20090804162943\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F57%2F17486338.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20090804162943&h=48655288&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00834f3dd04a441fbac24b646c268442545c0436","tid":1905731,"uid":235465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"同哥狗豬一場會令球隊清醒一樣<br />\n又贏"},{"pid":"2986a2d99baaea34247b2e175e7b0a47dbeb6678","tid":1905731,"uid":204475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ad29b68743348b3b538ddd194319525f904ab2","tid":1905731,"uid":196552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"聯賽44連勝<br />\n曼聯慘被無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77f8c40ea97eab64f449b49dcdb890a8f633541","tid":1905731,"uid":232575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76ad29b68743348b3b538ddd194319525f904ab2","tid":1905731,"uid":196552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"聯賽44連勝<br />\n曼聯慘被無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"其實係宿敵愛華頓成功絕殺我利個英超冠軍<br />\n<br />\n無人想理曼聯個場和波"},{"pid":"934316f62cfa235d49dd513840a9580543b4e4d1","tid":1905731,"uid":67225,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:49:31.000Z","msg":"我信高普真心唔在意<br />\n但呢度班利狗我就唔信了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239fb059429e185b9ade66140fc1025a19709a8